headline: Vibrant Emotional Health Welcomes Three New Members to Board of Directors to Help Advance National Mental Health Access and Innovation
summary: Vibrant Emotional Health (Vibrant), one of the nation's leading mental health organizations, is proud to welcome three distinguished leaders, Bethany Baran, Trip Hofer, and Gregory Phalin, to its Board of Directors. Their appointments reflect Vibrant's commitment to expanding inclusive, accessible mental health support to meet the urgent and growing needs of communities that need us most.
